com.mostc.pftt.model.phpt
Class ReadOnlyPhpIni

java.lang.Object
  com.mostc.pftt.model.phpt.PhpIni
      com.mostc.pftt.model.phpt.ReadOnlyPhpIni

public class ReadOnlyPhpIni
extends PhpIni

A PhpIni that can not be edited. Attempts to edit (such as calling #putSingle) are silently ignored. No exceptions are thrown.

Author:
Matt Ficken
